Introduction  

The purpose of this assignment was to develop a GUI based weekly expense tracker using Java. This application allows the user to record and manage their weekly expenses by selecting days, category, amount, and descriptions for the expenses.  

This application was developed using Java swing for GUI. The main goal was to provide a simple and user friendly way for users to track their spending habits during the week. 

 

System design 

This program was required to include the below 

. Dropdown menu for day selection 

. Dropdown menu for category  

. Amount field  

. Description Field  

. Add expense button  

. Button to calculate weekly expense  

. Button to display expense grouped by category  

. Error handling input 

